Benito, son of rapper and TV producer, Abdulrasheed Bello AKA JJC Skillz, has reacted to his father’s alleged remarriage. Bello was said to have reportedly remarried barely eight months after their separation from popular actress, Funke Akindele. He allegedly got married last month to Kogi-born Falilat Raji in a secret ceremony which held in Kano State. A supposed wedding invitation with the rapper’s name and his new wife also surfaced on the internet. Reacting to the news, Benito who’s also the son of JJCSkillz’s second baby mama, Mella aka Snoop Mummy felt sorry for his father’s new wife who he numbered as the hundredth. “Wifey number 100, Kmt I feel sorry for her,” he wrote.